name: Shannon Hines
text: Great pizza choices, well priced lunch buffet with grey choices.  They have a salad bar and video game room as well.  A bit pricey.

name: Greg Montano
text: Tuesday night buffets are the best:  Board games, fantastic salad bar and pizzas, wonderful family time.  Super helpful and friendly staff,  Round Table is the king of pizza!

name: Carol Boller
text: My husband and I went today with our little one for the buffet. Everything was extremely clean and the food was great. The manager (Felisha I believe was her name) was very nice and helpful. We will be back soon.

name: bill fern
text: Very sad, pizza is fine ..it's the management, I called and had pizza delivered to my house 3weeks ago... they took over an 1 1/2 hr to deliver.. the manager promised me a free large pizza next time I called.. so I call today to get free …More

name: You don’t Know
text: This was the worst pizza I have ever had.  The dough was undercooked and soggy there was barely any toppings on it and the parmesan bread twists tasted like dough no flavor at all.  For $46 I expected a whole lot better then this.  I definitely will not be going back.  Very disappointed.
